[{"date":"1949-10-22","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/b5/7e/275357_3iooq.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/b5/7e/275357_3iooq.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/b5/7e/275357_3iooq.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/b5/7e/275357_3iooq.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/b5/7e/275357_3iooq.jpg"},"summary":"　　这一天，汤姆有杀气腾腾地守在杰瑞的洞前，准备好好戏耍这个小家伙。可是收音机里的一条新闻让他打消了念头，原来今天开始就是爱护小动物纪念周，主持人提倡大家用爱心呵护身边的小生命。汤姆心有所动，移去了洞前的陷阱，转而取来鲜花、礼品和美味的蛋糕。他诚心诚意“敲门”，可是里面全没有动静。好奇的汤姆伸进洞里张望，发现杰瑞此时并不在家，而桌子上一本日记引起了他的注意。他拿出来翻阅，里面记满了杰瑞和汤姆日常打闹的趣事，比如草皮横飞的高尔夫球大战（Tee for Two）、险些把杰瑞夹死的捉鼠指南（Mouse Trouble）、火光四溅的烟花对攻（The Yankee Doodle Mouse）等。 \r\n　　汤姆起初看得哈哈大笑，可是似乎日记本里全是关于他的糗事，令他颇为不爽……","name":"Jerry's Diary","name_cn":"杰瑞的日记","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":18,"total_cont":0},{"name":"欧美","count":9,"total_cont":0},{"name":"猫和老鼠","count":8,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1949","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":4,"total_cont":0},{"name":"米高梅","count":3,"total_cont":0},{"name":"原创","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1940s","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"5(0)","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1940-1949","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版-02","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Short_film","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"杰瑞的日记"},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1949-10-22"},{"key":"片长","value":"6分23秒"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":34,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":1,"4":1,"5":4,"6":12,"7":13,"8":3,"9":0,"10":0},"score":6.3},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":1,"dropped":4,"wish":3,"collect":85,"doing":1},"id":275357,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["剧场版"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1949-10-07","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/88/b7/542372_cxw44.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/88/b7/542372_cxw44.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/88/b7/542372_cxw44.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/88/b7/542372_cxw44.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/88/b7/542372_cxw44.jpg"},"summary":"一望无际、寒冷宁静的南极冰原上，突然钻出了穿着泳装的兔八哥（梅尔·布兰科 Mel Blanc 配音）。兔八哥原打算去迈阿密的海边游泳，甚至还带了遮阳伞和防晒霜，谁知在地底下打洞时走错了路，阴差阳错来到了南极。他先是跳到冰冷的海里几乎被冻死，然后又险些遭到爱斯基摩猎人的袭击。这里显然没有什么值得留恋的，兔八哥打算前往迈阿密，不过全被一只萌兮兮的小企鹅挡住去路。他想方设法要摆脱这个缠人的小家伙，结果小企鹅竟被猎人抓走。良心不安的兔八哥无法就这么离开，他必须在此之前从猎人手里救回小企鹅。为此，兔八哥和凶暴的猎人展开连番激战……","name":"Frigid Hare","name_cn":"兔八哥去南极","tags":[{"name":"短片","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"美国","count":2,"total_cont":0},{"name":"Chuck.Jones","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"华纳","count":1,"total_cont":0},{"name":"1949","count":1,"total_cont":0}],"infobox":[{"key":"中文名","value":"兔八哥去南极"},{"key":"别名","value":[{"v":"兔八哥之南极兔八哥"}]},{"key":"上映年度","value":"1949年10月7日"},{"key":"片长","value":"7分钟"},{"key":"导演","value":"Chuck Jones"},{"key":"编剧","value":"Michael Maltese"},{"key":"话数","value":"1"}],"rating":{"rank":0,"total":3,"count":{"1":0,"2":0,"3":0,"4":1,"5":0,"6":1,"7":1,"8":0,"9":0,"10":0},"score":5.7},"total_episodes":0,"collection":{"on_hold":1,"dropped":1,"wish":1,"collect":8,"doing":0},"id":542372,"eps":1,"meta_tags":["短片","美国"],"volumes":0,"series":false,"locked":false,"nsfw":false,"type":2},{"date":"1949-10-05","platform":"剧场版","images":{"small":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/200/pic/cover/l/05/13/64093_Bs0Si.jpg","grid":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/100/pic/cover/l/05/13/64093_Bs0Si.jpg","large":"https://lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/l/05/13/64093_Bs0Si.jpg","medium":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/800/pic/cover/l/05/13/64093_Bs0Si.jpg","common":"https://lain.bgm.tv/r/400/pic/cover/l/05/13/64093_Bs0Si.jpg"},"summary":"       这是迪斯尼的第11部经典中篇合辑剧情动画片，两个段落中的“小蟾蜍”改编自Kenneth Grahame 的原著《The Wind in the Willows》“瞌睡谷传奇”则改编自 Washington Irving 著作《The Sketch Book》中同名故事","name":"The Adventures of Ichabod and Mr. Toad","name_cn":"伊老师与小蟾蜍大历险","tags":[{"name":"迪士尼","count":6,"total_cont":0},{"name":"剧场版","count"